- Workflow output surfaces run_id/scenario_id links so investigators can jump directly to relevant evidence.","notes":"CI matrix workflow consumes the canonical orchestrator manifest (bd-mblr.4.5.2) plus artifact schema so lane definition remains deterministic and drift-resistant. Treat artifact durability as first-class; missing artifacts on failure should itself fail the job.","status":"in_progress","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:08.647642001Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T08:45:01.068606028Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.3.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:08.647642001Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.3.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:38.966556362Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.4.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:38.464845668Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.2.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.5.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T01:33:45.626266368Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
